outputs.output_descr: SWARGA is a joint initiative between UNDP and the Ministry of Women's Empowerment and Child Protection, and builds on previous UNDP efforts to document and analyse the general situation of women's participation in politics and government in Indonesia.  The project will run from 2012 to 2015.
